pes) Added post types of <code>Molongui Author Box</code> plugin to the hidden types array.</li>\n<li>(Builders/Elementor) Added language switcher for Elementor v.3.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>2020-08-24 &#8211; version 2.5.2</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>(Vendor/ACF) Added filter for the Image field type. (Note: Multilingual value will be accessible in the &#8220;Builder&#8221; mode.)</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Thank you for your continuing support! Please enjoy the new release and do not hesitate to contact us should you have any questions.</h3>\n<h3>FYI: Please read <a href=\"https://wpglobus.com/faq/when-i-save-one-language-everything-published-in-the-other-language-disappears/\">FAQ</a></h3>\n<hr />\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/WPGlobus/WPGlobus/blob/master/CHANGELOG.md\" rel=\"nofollow\">The complete history of changes</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/wpglobus/\">Download Free WPGlobus Multilingual WordPress Plugin!</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wpglobus.com/plugin-updates/wpglobus-update/\">WPGlobus 2.5.3</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://wpglobus.com\">WPGlobus</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:2;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:63:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n\n					\n										\n					\n		\n		\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:3:{s:0:\"\";a:6:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"WPGlobus for WooCommerce 3.5.13\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:77:\"https://wpglobus.com/plugin-updates/woocommerce-wpglobus-update-%f0%9f%8c%90/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\