 experience as an excellent buyer and seller have set me up to succeed in this role. I have successful experience in the wholesale, retail, on-line directions, experience in import and export of goods, air and sea cargo.  I have experience in inventory management and analytics, compliance with deadlines for closing receivables and budget execution.  I have good organizational skills, good knowledge in personnel management - 30 people.  I concluded more than 120 profitable contracts.  I have many years of experience in countries such as Dubai, Qatar, Thailand, Bangladesh, Cambodia, Bangkok. I was maintaining the business contacts in companies in Mumbai, Delhi, Kolkata (India), Dhaka (Bangladesh), Nimbo (China), Karachi (Pakistan), Dheira (Dubai), Doha (Qatar).  I have over come the language barrier (Russian and Ukrainian), I study languages in the process of work.  Fluent in English, Hindi, Marathi, Urdu, Punjabi. \r\nI earned respect from the staff and management through effective communication and business relations.  I was awarded the “Outstanding Achievements” trophy for my willingness to play an active and practical role in every job related duty.\r\n I am ready to provide contacts of my former employers who will be able to discuss with you my positive attitude and strong work ethic. Thank you for your consideration, and I’m looking forward to discussing this opportunity with you in an interview setting.\r\n\r\nRegards,\r\nRiyaz Qureshi\r\n+380688669011\r\nqureshiriyaz.work@gmail.com\r\n \r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n'),(10772,675,'_field_vacancy','Sales Executive'),(10773,675,'_field_cf-file','Riyaz_CV-sales.pdf'),(10774,675,'_fields','a:7:{s:7:\"cf-name\";N;s:10:\"cf-surname\";N;s:8:\"cf-email\";N;s:8:\"cf-phone\";N;s:10:\"cf-message\";N;s:7:\"vacancy\";N;s:7:\"cf-file\";N;}'),(10775,675,'_meta','a:19:{s:13:\"serial_number\";i:166;s:9:\"remote_ip\";s:10:\"172.18.0.7\";s:10:\"user_agent\";s:132:\"Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko