erfaces);</li>\r\n 	<li>Support the project at all stages of its development;</li>\r\n 	<li>Creation of illustrations, infographics, icons if necessary;</li>\r\n 	<li>Communication with the developer;</li>\r\n 	<li>Sometimes communication with the client;</li>\r\n 	<li>Stay up to date with design trends.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2>We guarantee:</h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Comfortable office;</li>\r\n 	<li>Friendly staff;</li>\r\n 	<li>Opportunity to develop professionally;</li>\r\n 	<li>Attending design conferences and parties;</li>\r\n 	<li>Decent reward for work.</li>\r\n</ul>{:}','{:uk}Web (UI/UX) дизайнер для створення сайтів та мобільних додатків{:}{:en}Web (UI / UX) designer for creating websites and mobile applications{:}','{:uk}Ми шукаємо дизайнера UI \\ UX, для роботи над мобільними та десктопними інтерфейсами для вирішення різноманітних користувацьких завдань.{:}{:en}We are looking for a UI \\ UX designer to work on mobile and desktop interfaces to solve various user tasks.{:}','publish','closed','closed','','web-ui-ux-dyzajner-dlya-stvorennya-sajtiv-ta-mobilnyh-dodatkiv','','','2020-09-17 15:00:54','2020-09-17 13:00:54','',0,'https://onix.kr.ua/?post_type=vacancies&#038;p=124',0,'vacancies','',0),(126,2,'2018-01-25 10:04:39','2018-01-25 10:04:39','','photo_2018-01-25_12-04-21','','inherit','closed','closed','','photo_2018-01-25_12-04-21','','','2018-01-25 10:04:39','2018-01-25 10:04:39','',59,'https://onix.kr.ua/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/photo_2018-01-25_12-04-21.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(131,2,'2018-02-20 14:15:43','2018-02-20 14:15:43','','Logo + Slogan White','','inherit','closed','closed','','logo-slogan-white','','','2018-02-20 14:15:43','2018-02-20 14:15:43','',0,'https://onix.kr.ua/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/Logo-Slogan-White.psd',0,'attachment','application/octet-stream',0),(132,2,'2018-02-20 14:15:57','2018-02-20 14:15:57','','Onix-Systems Logo','','inherit','closed','closed','','logo-slogan-white-2','','','2018-02-20 14:16:11','2018-02-20 14:16: