ctively developing</li>\n 	<li>Opportunity to adapt your day to your lifestyle</li>\n 	<li>Compensation for attending IT conferences</li>\n 	<li>Corporate outdoor recreation</li>\n 	<li>Endless coffee, cookies and lounge</li>\n</ul>{:}','{:uk}Unity Software Engineer{:}{:en}Unity Software Engineer{:}','{:uk}Компанія Onix шукає Unity Software Engineer у підтримку до існуючого проекту{:}{:en}Onix is looking for a Unity Software Engineer to support an existing project{:}','inherit','closed','closed','','96-autosave-v1','','','2020-09-17 15:03:55','2020-09-17 13:03:55','',96,'https://onix.kr.ua/96-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(975,1,'2020-09-17 15:05:59','2020-09-17 13:05:59','','{:uk}Вакансії{:}{:en}Vacanc{:}','','publish','closed','closed','','vakansiyi','','','2020-09-17 15:13:30','2020-09-17 13:13:30','',0,'https://onix.kr.ua/?page_id=975',0,'page','',0),(976,1,'2020-09-17 15:05:59','2020-09-17 13:05:59','','Вакансії','','inherit','closed','closed','','975-revision-v1','','','2020-09-17 15:05:59','2020-09-17 13:05:59','',975,'https://onix.kr.ua/975-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(977,1,'2020-09-17 15:07:50','2020-09-17 13:07:50','','Вакансії','','inherit','closed','closed','','975-revision-v1','','','2020-09-17 15:07:50','2020-09-17 13:07:50','',975,'https://onix.kr.ua/975-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(980,1,'2020-09-17 15:13:08','2020-09-17 13:13:08','','{:uk}Вакансії{:}{:en}Vacanc{:}','','inherit','closed','closed','','975-revision-v1','','','2020-09-17 15:13:08','2020-09-17 13:13:08','',975,'https://onix.kr.ua/975-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(981,1,'2020-09-17 15:13:08','2020-09-17 13:13:08','','{:uk}Вакансії{:}{:en}Vacanc{:}','','inherit','closed','closed','','975-revision-v1','','','2020-09-17 15:13:08','2020-09-17 13:13:08','',975,'https://onix.kr.ua/975-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(982,1,'2020-09-17 15:13:30','2020-09-17 13:13:30','','{:uk}Вакансії{:}{:en}Vacanc{:}','','inherit','closed','closed','','975-revision-v1','','','2020-09-17 15:13